{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": 0, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7379, "name_id": 1, "pid": 2886, "text": "国应该和“郭”“廓”是同源的，是城郭、城池的意思。“国人”最早指的是城里人，和“野人”即郊外的田野上的人区别。", "timestamp": 1639720775}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7383, "name_id": 2, "pid": 2886, "text": "Re Alice: “国人”是否都是贵族？", "timestamp": 1639721022}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7385, "name_id": 2, "pid": 2886, "text": "Re Alice: “国人暴动”是大小贵族的暴动么？", "timestamp": 1639721071}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7390, "name_id": 3, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Alice: 从谐声关系上看，“国”与“域”同源，与“郭”不同源。此外将“国”与“家”并列很明显是“诸侯领”与“大夫领”的并列。", "timestamp": 1639721178}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7391, "name_id": 4, "pid": 2886, "text": "Re Bob: 不一定，国人就是城里人，城里人也有商人、手工业者", "timestamp": 1639721224}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7394, "name_id": 3, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Bob: “居住在国的人”。", "timestamp": 1639721258}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7395, "name_id": 3, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Alice: 谔谔，什么农逼右书说", "timestamp": 1639721289}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7396, "name_id": 3, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Alice: 我手边就有白一平的《上古汉语音手册》和沙加尔的《上古汉语新构拟》，不清楚学界研究的就别乱说。", "timestamp": 1639721411}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7398, "name_id": 1, "pid": 2886, "text": "Re Bob: 我在吕思勉的《中国通史》上说国建在山上，里面是异族统治者，也就是百姓，国外是田野平地，是黎民在耕作。国人靠着奴役野人的耕作而活，这是很早之前的国家形式（挺像山大王的）。似乎这这个意思，很久之前看的。", "timestamp": 1639721445}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7404, "name_id": 1, "pid": 2886, "text": "Re Carol: 我找自己的理解说的，确实没参考什么", "timestamp": 1639721557}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7414, "name_id": 5, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Alice: 你有这种想法还是很好的，在某种程度上是正确的，但是你忽视了语音流变，比如“国”在中古是闭音节，“锅”在中古是开音节，不会同源。要想确保古汉语中读音相似，可以通过相同的声旁，这就是“右书说”。", "timestamp": 1639721938}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7418, "name_id": 5, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Alice: 比如“國”的声旁与“域”相同，含义相近，就可以推测它们同源。", "timestamp": 1639722113}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7493, "name_id": 6, "pid": 2886, "text": "学到了好多", "timestamp": 1639725900}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7495, "name_id": 6, "pid": 2886, "text": "诸侯领  这个词怎么理解呢", "timestamp": 1639725970}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7502, "name_id": 7, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Francis: 诸侯的领地", "timestamp": 1639726693}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7667, "name_id": 8, "pid": 2886, "text": "Re Francis: 学到个狗屁，他说的话你得好好考证考证。前几期已经发了一堆扯淡玩意了", "timestamp": 1639738975}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7680, "name_id": 9, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Hans: 看任何简体中文来源的信息都需要好好考证，不止是我的。", "timestamp": 1639739692}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7763, "name_id": 8, "pid": 2886, "text": "Re Isabella: 看任何信息都要好好考证。只是你之前的错误太多我才提醒ta的", "timestamp": 1639743567}, {"author_title": null, "blocked": false, "can_del": false, "cid": 7768, "name_id": 10, "pid": 2886, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Hans: 到底什么错误呢？“用拳头收割”的讲法有些问题，因为“权”和“利”是并列关系，应当要说成“拳头与收割”比较好。其它的洞我是不觉得有什么错误。", "timestamp": 1639743836}], "cw": null, "likenum": 10, "pid": 2886, "poll": null, "reply": 19, "text": "[tmp]\n#比较语源学\n#天空到来\n英语country来自法语contree，来自拉丁语contrata“面对的土地”。\n汉语“国家”，“国”是“诸侯领”，“家”是“士大夫领”，“贵族领地”。", "timestamp": 1639709549, "type": "text", "url": null}}